Path: Flags
Content:
``--modifiers, -m``
: List of modifiers.
``--keycodes, -k``
: List of keycodes.
``--modes, -o``
: List of edit modes.
``--events, -e``
: List of reedline event.
``--edits, -d``
: List of edit commands.
