’Ł@886a2d8f90e44b7cfce1e4382d1d4596869b2e63856dc87a3b3dd9bf6051c8e5ŚRTitle: title: keybindings list
Path: Examples
Content:
Get list of key modifiers
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> keybindings list --modifiers


```
Get list of reedline events and edit commands
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> keybindings list -e -d


```
Get list with all the available options
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> keybindings list


```
